Do you want me to try downloading it?

Downloading ru.utf-8.spl...
:!curl &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;'http://ftp.vim.org/pub/vim/runtime/spell/ru.utf-8.spl'&lt;/span&gt; -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;'/var/folders/m8/r3crydz15ygbg8y6q5fpw_xh0000gp/T/vun2CXm/0.spl'&lt;/span&gt;
  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current
                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed
&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;/var/folders/m8/r3crydz15ygbg8y6q5fpw_xh0000gp/T/vun2CXm/0.spl&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;noeol] 1280L, 837741C
